<h1>Title here: {{title}}</h1>
<p>Welcome to <em>LocalLibrary</em>, a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.
</p>

  {{#if error}}
    <p>Error getting dynamic content.</p>
  {{else}}
    <p>The library has the following record counts</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Books: {{data.book_count}} </strong></li>
        <li><strong>Copies: {{data.book_instance_count}} </strong></li>
        <li><strong>Copies: {{data.book_instance_available_count}} </strong></li>
        <li><strong>Authors: {{data.author_count}} </strong></li>
        <li><strong>Genres: {{data.genre_count}} </strong></li>
    </ul>
  {{/if}}